description:
Danny welcomes Casey Wilson (actress/writer/co-host of the Bitch Sesh podcast) to talk ALL things Bravo. They chat about last week's flawless episode of #RHONY, this season of #RHOBH, Southern Charm, Casey's illustrious career, a Happy Endings reboot, working with Regina Hall, plus they do a Bravo lightning round featuring Bravolebrities of past and present, and so much more.


Casey: 2:33ish
